## Changelog #25
**Server is now running on Minecraft version 26.1.2**

### Changes:
- Daycycle length is now 40 Minutes
- Deep Blue Dimension now extends to y -16 to prevent players from falling into the void when the portal creation fails
- Master librarians in KS Villages now can sell maps to KS Structures
- Novice villagers in KS Villages can have a new thematic trade
- Shields are now enchantable in Enchanting Tables
- Removed Baby Name Tag functionality to keep Mobs as Babies
- Removed custom Name Tag recipe
- Added Chicken Coop and Pig Pen structures
- Added recipe to turn Charcoal into Black Dye
- Added Acacia, Birch, Cherry, Dark Oak, Jungle, Mangrove, Oak, Pale Oak & Spruce Logs as possible Trade for Fletchers (Level 1)
- Added Treasure Enchantments (from Enchantments Encore) as possible Trade for Librarians (Level 5)
- Added Scrolls as possible Trade for Librarians (Level 1)
- Added Biome Brews as possible Trade for Clerics (Level 5)
- Added Boiled Eggs as possible Trade for Farmers (Level 1)
- Added Apple & Chorus Pies as possible Trade for Farmers (Level 2)
- Added Cheese & Sweet Berry Cookies as possible Trade for Farmers (Level 3)
- Added Golden Beetroots, Chrous Fruits, Potatoes & Sweet Berries as possible Trade for Farmers (Level 5)
- Added Invisible Item Frames as possible Trade for Cartographers (Level 4)
- Added Waypoint Lock as possible Villager Trade for Cartographers (Level 1)
- Added Portal Horn as possible Villager Trade for Cartographers (Level 5)
- Added some Waypoint Hubs as possible Trade for Cartographers (Level 2):
    - Savanna Type: Acacia Waypoint Hub
    - Jungle Type: Jungle Waypoint Hub
    - Swamp Type: Mangrove Waypoint Hub
    - Plains Type: Oak Waypoint Hub
    - Desert Type: Sandstone Waypoint Hub
    - Taiga & Snow Type: Spruce Waypoint Hub
- Frog Feeder now emit a block update when Food Mobs are being spawned
- Waypoint Hubs now emit a block update whenever someone teleports to them
- Added Frozen Frog variant (Can be bred in Ice Spike Biomes. Drops Ice when eating)
- Added Cold Yellow Cow variant (Spawns in the same biomes as Vanilla Cold variant)
- Added Warm Brown Cow variant (Spawns in the same biomes as Vanilla warm variant)
- Added Sniffer Cow variant (Spawns in Sunflower Plains & Flower Forests. Drops Torchflower/Pitcher Plant)
- Added Goose Chicken variant (Spawns in Old Growth Spruce/Pine Taiga & Dark Forest biomes)
- Added Swamp Zombie Nautilus variant (Spawns in Swamp & Mangrove Swamp biomes)
- Added Flamingo Chicken variant (spawns in Beach biomes)
- Added Penguin Chicken variant (spawns in Snowy Beach biomes)
- Added Potato variants for Cows, Chickens and Pigs (spawn in/with Potato Farm structures)
- Added Potato Farm structure (generates in Plains & Sunflower Plains biomes)
- Wandering Trader Mob variants now spawn less often with a Wandering Trader
- Added Livestock Breeder Block:
    - Can be crafted from 8 Hay Blocks and a Barrel
    - When placed makes Livestock Animals (Sheeps, Pigs, Rabbits, Cows, Chickens) breed every 10 minutes
    - Emits a block update whenever breeding has started
- Added "Baby" textures for Armadillo Chestplate
- Added "Baby" textures for Crown of Roots
- Added "Baby" textures for Armor of Roots
- Added "Baby" textures for Reinforced Armor of Roots
- Added "Baby" textures for Allay Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Bee Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Creaking Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Enderman Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Ghast Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Husk Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Iron Golem Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Phantom Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for Stray Shell
- Added "Baby" textures for all custom Mob Variants (Cat, Chicken, Cow, Pig, Wolf)
- Updated Textures for Timber Wolf variant
- Changed & improved how custom sounds for Mob variants work:
    - Mob Variants with custom sounds now play them like vanilla Mobs
    - Creeper Cat variant now uses Creeper Mob sounds for some of its sounds
    - Sniffer Cow variant uses Sniffer Mob sounds
    - Creaking Wolf variant now use Creaking Mob Sounds
    - Ender Pig, Chicken, Cow variants now use a mix of Enderman & Endermite sounds
    - Skeleton Cat, Chicken, Cow, Pig, Wolf variants now use Skeleton sounds
    - Strider Chicken variant now uses Strider sounds
    - Rooster Chicken variants crowing sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults
    - Pigeons Chicken variants cooing sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults
    - Ostrich Chicken variants grunting sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults
    - Duck Chicken variants quacking sound is now it's natural ambient sound for adults

### Fixes:
- Crab Claw description saying Max Level is 5 instead of 3
- Fixed Villager Info not working properly
- Rarity Mob Treasure Bundles not being filled sometimes
- Cold White Cow variant using the wrong tag list for biomes to spawn in
- Dark Brown Chicken variants spawn biomes not set correctly
- Added missing lang key for Pigeon Egg
- Potentially fixed a bug where Village Names change regularly